sentences.sContent: Carbon monoxide is released when carbon in fuel—both plants and fossil fuels like gasoline—burns incompletely.
sentences.sContent_eng: Carbon monoxide is released when carbon in fuel—both plants and fossil fuels like gasoline—burns incompletely.
sentences.sCn: 当作为燃料的碳——包括植物和化石燃料比如汽油——不完全燃烧时，就会产生一氧化碳。

sentences.sContent: The researchers found that the effect of soot, which is incompletely burned fuel, would dwarf that of the carbon dioxide emissions from the launches.
sentences.sContent_eng: The researchers found that the effect of soot, which is incompletely burned fuel, would dwarf that of the carbon dioxide emissions from the launches.
sentences.sCn: 研究者发现，燃料不完全燃烧产生的烟尘，会使发射过程中产生的二氧化碳的排放量减少。
